'''冰島－印度關係'''，是指[[冰島共和國|冰島共和國]]和[[印度共和國|印度共和國]]之間的雙邊關係。歷史上，冰島和印度兩國的關係一直友好，但缺乏實質性的合作<ref name="My background helps me: Kalam ">{{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2005/05/30/stories/2005053014431200.htm|title=My background helps me: Kalam|first=K.V. Prasad|date=2005-05-30|publisher=The Hindu|accessdate=2008-09-28|archive-date=2006-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060301155448/http://www.hindu.com/2005/05/30/stories/2005053014431200.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
冰島和印度於1975年建交。印度在冰島於[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[大使館|大使館]]設有代表，而印度亦在[[挪威|挪威]][[奧斯陸|奧斯陸]]設大使館。自2005年起，兩國開始加強外交和經濟關係<ref name="Inauguration of the Embassy of Iceland in New Delhi" />；該年，[[冰島總統|冰島總統]][[格里姆松|格里姆松]]首次到印度的外訪，又承諾支持印度成為[[聯合國安理會常任理事國|聯合國安理會常任理事國]]之一，是第一個有如此表態的[[北歐|北歐]]國家；時任[[印度總統|印度總統]][[阿卜杜勒·卡拉姆|阿卜杜勒·卡拉姆]]於2005年5月又到冰島進行正式訪問<ref name="My background helps me: Kalam " />。其後，冰島於2006年在印度[[新德里|新德里]]設置新的大使館<ref name="Inauguration of the Embassy of Iceland in New Delhi">{{cite web |url=http://www.iceland.org/in/the-embassy/news-and-events/nr/1748 |title=Inauguration of the Embassy of Iceland in New Delhi |date=2006-02-26 |publisher=Icelandic Foreign Service |accessdate=2008-09-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061003172058/http://www.iceland.org/in/the-embassy/news-and-events/nr/1748 |archivedate=2006-10-03 }}</ref>。[[印度海軍|印度海軍]]亦曾派員參觀冰島<ref name="Indian Navy Team in Iceland">{{cite web |url=http://www.iceland.org/in/the-embassy/news-and-events/nr/2929 |title=Indian Navy Team in Iceland |date=2006-08-25 |publisher=Icelandic Foreign Service |accessdate=2008-09-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081203003017/http://www.iceland.org./in/the-embassy/news-and-events/nr/2929 |archivedate=2008-12-03 }}</ref>。[[貢納爾·保爾|貢納爾·保爾]]松是現任[[冰島駐印度大使|冰島駐印度大使]]<ref name="About the Embassy">{{cite web |url=http://www.iceland.org/in/the-embassy/about-the-embassy/ |title=About the Embassy |publisher=Icelandic Foreign Service |accessdate=2008-09-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080928072152/http://www.iceland.org/in/the-embassy/about-the-embassy/ |archivedate=2008-09-28 }}</ref>，[[S·納坦|S·納坦]]則是[[印度駐冰島大使|印度駐冰島大使]]<ref name="Shri S. Swaminathan to be India’s first resident Ambassador to Iceland">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090410162813/http://meaindia.nic.in/pressrelease/2008/09/03pr01.htm|url=http://meaindia.nic.in/pressrelease/2008/09/03pr01.htm|title=Shri S. Swaminathan to be India’s first resident Ambassador to Iceland|date=September 3, 2008|publisher=NIC India Ministry of External Affairs, New Delhi|accessdate=2008-09-28|archivedate=2009-04-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
